  "remarks": "\nFormer Deputy Prosecutor General, appointed by the Constituent Assembly. Responsible for undermining democracy and the rule of law, including by initiating politically-motivated prosecutions and failing to investigate allegations of human rights violations by the Maduro regime. In a previous role as National Public Prosecutor, she admitted to carrying out her duties with “political bias”.",
